item.azur_lane_mc.set001_walls.tooltip: Mold... mold everywhere! Should we just tear this down?
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_bed.tooltip: Too cheap to even buy a blanket, eh?
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_decor_a.tooltip: Today's soup is... clear, flavorless, and vegetarian.
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_decor_b.tooltip: Everyone needs time to relax and enjoy some fresh tea!
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_decor_c.tooltip: Works well enough to catch rain from the leaky roof!
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_decor_d.tooltip: This cat hasn't caught a mouse in its entire life.
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_door.tooltip: This sliding door is so hard to close, we usually keep it wide open.
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_floordecor.tool: A tattered and shredded mat. Really unties the room.
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_lighting_a.tool: Petrified so that we can save electricity!
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_lighting_b.tool: The night is most beautiful by candlelight.
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_lighting_c.tool: The strength of our spirits are like the flames of a fire in darkness!
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_prop_a.tooltip: Is it really a screen if you can see through the holes in it?
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_prop_b.tooltip: An old TV purchased at the local thrift shop.
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_prop_c.tooltip: This should be good enough to clean up the puddles from last night's rain.
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_prop_d.tooltip: We should grow our own vegetables to eat and save money!
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_seat_a.tooltip: A pile of old newspapers makes a good cushion when necessary.
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_seat_b.tooltip: This will have to do for now!
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_storage.tooltip: Clothes are expensive! You gotta protect them!
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_table.tooltip: Cardboard is wonderful! It works for everything!
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_walldecor_a.too: A good spot for roommates to leave notes for each other.
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_walldecor_b.too: Write on paper instead of the wall!
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_walldecor_c.too: This will have to make do as decoration for now.
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_walldecor_d.too: Not many sounds come through except a few pops and crackles.
item.azur_lane_mc.set001_window.tooltip: The view outside isn't too bad, but it doesn't seem to keep the bugs outside.
